  - Title: Maitri Upanishad
    Location: VI 34
Tags:
  - Combat-Action=Metanoia=‘Duo Sunt in Homine’
Format: verse
---
Sarhsâra is just one’s own thought：
With effort he should cleanse it, then.
What is one’s thought, that he becomes;
This is the eternal mystery.
